gameRecap.title: Game Recap: 76ers 121, Hornets 114
gameRecap.excerpt: The 76ers defeated the Hornets, 121-114. Tyrese Maxey (33 points, six rebounds, five assists, five 3PM) and Tobias Harris (31 points, 12 rebounds, five 3PM) combine for 64 points for the 76ers in the victory, while Miles Bridges tallied 27 points, 11 rebounds and five 3PM for the Hornets in the losing effort. The 76ers improve to 34-25 on the season, while the Hornets fall to 15-45.
